Package: rviber
Type: Package
Title: AI Vibe Coder for RStudio — Chat, Generate, Fix and Run R Code
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Your Name", email = "you@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: An AI-powered coding assistant that lives inside RStudio.
    Supports Groq, Gemini, OpenAI, Anthropic, Ollama, Mistral, and any
    OpenAI-compatible provider. Chat with AI about your code, generate R
    scripts from plain English, fix errors, explain selected code, autocomplete
    the next lines, run and debug code, and generate ggplot2 charts — all
    without leaving RStudio.
